      <bioghist id="aspace_29a3f71f900c24a9bf9b30cdbe1f7635">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Vance R. Dittman graduated from Yale College in 1924 and the Yale Law School in 1927.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_e3d620c3628746ad99e51ff26a642199">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of miscellaneous memorabilia of Vance R. Dittman, Jr. (Yale 1924). Also included are creative works by Catherine Pierson Dittman (wife of Vance Dittman), who studied painting at Yale, and Dean B. Lyman.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
  
